<h3 id="validation-error-status-code-400">Validation Error Status Code: 400 <a class="headerlink" href="validation-errors-test#validation-error-status-code-400" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h3>
<p>Ok, design time! Writing the test is our time to <em>think</em> about how each endpoint
should work. Since we're not sending a <code>username</code>,  what status code should the endpoint
return? Use 400:</p>
